    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Titanium Silver. This S54-powered masterpiece features individual throttle bodies and dual VANOS, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critically, this example has undergone full subframe reinforcement and a proactive rod bearing replacement using VAC coated bearings. The suspension retains its original kinematics with refreshed bushings, ensuring the chassis remains as taut as the day it left Regensburg. No pixel degradation in the instrument cluster or hydraulic leaks in the steering rack. A turn-key, high-revving icon for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
