      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) that serves as a benchmark for the chassis. This specimen features the S54B32 power plant, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system, all operating within factory tolerances. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual and a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed with surgical precision, including a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing replacement. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining all original VIN tags, while the interior displays zero UV degradation or bolster compression. A true turnkey collector piece for the purist.",
